'''乳房整型'''（Mammaplasty，也稱為mammoplasty<ref>{{cite web|title=mammoplasty|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/mammoplasty|publisher=The Free Dictionary|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205060624/https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/mammoplasty|dead-url=no}}</ref>或mastoplasty）是指以調整[[乳房|乳房]]形狀為目的的[[整型|整型]]手術，主要可以分為以下幾種<ref>{{cite web|last1=Horndeski|first1=Gary|title=mammaplasty (mammoplasty) surgical procedures|url=http://horndeski.com/mammaplasty-surgical-procedures/|publisher=Horndeski Method|accessdate=10 February 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210213447/http://horndeski.com/mammaplasty-surgical-procedures/|archivedate=2015年2月10日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Breast Procedures|url=http://www.wakehealth.edu/School/Plastic-and-Reconstructive-Surgery/Breast-Procedures.htm|publisher=Wake Forest School of Medicine|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914035501/http://www.wakehealth.edu/School/Plastic-and-Reconstructive-Surgery/Breast-Procedures.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
#[[隆乳|隆乳]]一般是指增加乳房體積、調整乳房外形或是質感的手術，一般會用手術在乳房中植入像鹽水袋或是矽酮等[[植體|植體]]，也有植入自身脂肪的隆乳手術。
#[[縮胸|縮胸]]一般是指減少乳房體積、調整乳房外形或是質感的手術，一般會切除部份的乳房組織。
#{{le|乳房固定術|mastopexy}}主要是改善[[乳房下垂|乳房下垂]]的情形。
